{%- comment -%} Sticky-stack scroll effect for Why Syruvia + About this syrup. Cards pile on top of each other. Compact variant. {%- endcomment -%}
<style>
html,body{overflow-x:clip!important;overflow-y:visible!important}
html body .pd{overflow-x:clip!important;overflow-y:visible!important}
